Use Case: Add Provider
Context: The operator adds a provider to the software
Actors: Operator

Main Success Scenario:

	1. The operator is prompted to enter the provider information
	2. The software generates a new provider number for that provider
	3. The new provider information is displayed on screen

Extensions:
	1a. The operator entered incomplete or invalid information
		1a.1. The system displays an error message
		1a.2. The use case returns to step 1.